<opener><lb/>Viro <abbr>Illustr.</abbr> et <abbr>Doct.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>Nic.</abbr> <abbr>Bern.</abbr></rs></opener>
<p><lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>gre non feres, ut spero, quod hucusque distulerim responsionem ad humanissimam Tuam
       <lb/><rs key="B_1716-11-27_991170517050005501" type="letter">epistolam</rs>, quam <choice><abbr>d.</abbr><expan>die</expan></choice> <date when="1716-11-27">27. Nov.</date> ad me mittere voluisti una cum inclusa Parentis mei, pro
         <lb/>qua re gratias maximas Tibi ago. Distuli equidem istam responsionem tum quia per
       <lb/>totos hos pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teritos dies partim in audiendis Professor<subst><del>ibus</del><add>um Lectionibus</add></subst> partim in re domestica or<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dinanda occupatus fui; tum quia<del> ho</del> nondum certus eram<subst><del> quo</del><add> de</add></subst> die <add>quo</add> ingressum
          <pb facs="1361347" n="2"/>
<lb/>meum <subst><del>mihi</del><add>facturus</add></subst> <subst><del>sum</del><add>essem</add></subst>, quemque Tibi <del> sig</del> notum facturum me esse promiseram.
         <lb/><abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> Urbi Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>fectus<!-- persontag UP Padua--> concessit mihi diem vigesimam secundam hujus 
       <lb/>mensis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quidem incidit in tempus vacationum, adeo ut post primam illam
         <lb/>Lectionem ante secundam diem Januarii nullam amplius habiturus sim Lectio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem. Gratu<subst><del>m</del><add>s</add></subst> mihi quidem erit honor, quo me afficere vis, si negotia Tua <del>hoc</del>
<lb/>permittant <add>ut huc venias</add> sed Tibi ingratus labor, quia non nisi levia audies in meis Lectionibus.
  <lb/>Epistolium <rs type="person">mercatoris Basilieensis</rs> ad <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Westenapel</rs><!-- DM>Westenapel ist nicht eindeutig identifizierbar.<-->, quod per <rs type="person">Adgnatum</rs> meum
         <lb/>Tibi misi, Te accepisse ac <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Westenapel</rs><!-- DM>Westenapel ist nicht eindeutig identifizierbar.<--> tradidisse, cistamque tandem Vene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tias appulisse spero; quod si ita est, eam propediem expecto. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum ignoscas
         <lb/>rogo libertati me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tibi tam multum laboris et oneris imponere audet.
         <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#AE">Æ</g></orig><reg>Ae</reg></choice>des novas Te jam inhabitare credo, et ut feliciter posthac inhabites
       <lb/>opto. Ego cum <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">adgnato</rs> similiter in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>des <subst><del><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></del><add>ab</add></subst> <subst><del><abbr>D.</abbr></del><add><abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr></add></subst> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Marchione Poleno</rs> p<unclear>r</unclear>o me
       <lb/>conduct<subst><del><gap/></del><add>as</add></subst> <subst><del>con</del><add>discessi</add></subst>. </p><closer><salute><rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Adgnatus</rs> meus <add>debit<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></add> obsequii cultum Tibi defert; idem officii
        <lb/>genus apud <abbr>Ill.</abbr> et <abbr>Exc.</abbr> Dominam <rs key="pers_DE-588-1178493288" type="person">Labiam</rs> data occasione et meo et ipsius
        <lb/>nomine exequi ne graveris.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <choice><abbr>a.d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1716-12-11">11. Decembris 1716</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>